messages.message: on https://aihub-uat.internal.instabase.com/, in build when I create fields, I now have to create them one by one instead of quickly selecting 5 of the suggested ones. Is this intended and is the future way forward in build?

yes, this is the intended UI

this change is turned on by default for internal users in 24.18

the goal of this change is to increase discoverability of the field editor
